                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>as to his ecclesiastical duties above Parnas &amp;<lb/> adjunta as\n                                        you will perceive by our code of<lb/> laws—it should be so,\n                                        if we desire to have<lb/> Respectable men at our head</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I regret that any man having his dignity<lb/> as a\n                                        Minister in view could be found to offer<lb/> himself under\n                                        the propositions set forth. <persName>Mr\n                                        DeSola</persName><lb/> it appears has not yet known off the\n                                        trammels of<lb/> the <add>?</add> Congregation I pity him,\n                                        &amp; could never<lb/> bring myself to respect his\n                                        ministers, the other Gentlemen<lb/> I know little of</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">All these circumstances lend to detract from<lb/>\n                                        the dignity of our people. I wish as the Prophet says<lb/>\n                                        we would become wise.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I will send to <placeName>New York</placeName> for\n                                        the Asmoneon<lb/> with best wishes Remain yours truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">A Wolff</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
